Well I was thinking we should all do something more fun and go deep into theÂ unexplored catacombs. Now I know it's not exactly romantic, but once we see all the human bones and lightless rooms, you'll start wanting to go further. Think of it! Crawling on our hands and bellies into shoulder width spaces underneath shaky stone, the echoes of our voices going on for miles, the fingernail clawed scriptures....I mean, c'mon, someone bring the camera for Kodak moments!
